		    <li><a href="././heoa.html#0">The University of Illinois at Chicago Plan for Combating Unauthorized Distribution of Copyrighted Materials</a>
</li>
		    <li><a href="././heoa.html#1">The plan to effectively combat copyright infringement</a>
</li>
		</ul>
	    </td>
